OL,3,C'We couldn't have stopped Valdo
OL,4,CCalocane killing that night,' says
OL,5,Cpolice chief
OL,7,F"The vigil at the university was
OL,8,Femotional, but the one in the market
OL,9,Fsquare was overwhelming," he said.
